{"tid":1838583,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB：美國流感大爆發！6600人死亡！","createTime":"2020-01-24T05:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T06:35:29.000Z","uid":265902,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"26f1e26b306dfa7b1e42943ff21f71467fe45335","tid":1838583,"uid":265902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:31:27.000Z","msg":"轉自&quot;抵制TVB戰線&quot; <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=0c4fac1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb</a> <br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=2ec2b8c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/sayno2tvb</a> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bELTZc5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbELTZc5.jpg&h=63547fca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事實：(TVB表示睇唔到)<br />\n1⃣ 死亡率：<br />\n武漢肺炎：3% - 30%<br />\n美國流感：0.05%<br />\n相差高達600倍！(註1) <br />\n<br />\n2⃣ 武肺有個案6日快速致死<br />\n<br />\n3⃣ 武肺未有可靠治療方法<br />\n<br />\n4⃣ 中国每年8.8万人死于流感！<br />\n<br />\n5⃣ 美國流感6600人死，只是估算數字<br />\n<br />\n(註1) 以中國官方公佈數字計，確診830人，死亡25人，死亡率3%。根據坊間專家估計，大量死因難以鑑定是否由武肺導致；連同將官方疑似虛報少報的死亡數字計算在內，估計死亡人數為公怖25人的10倍，約250人死，死亡率為30%。<br />\n而美國流感死亡率己經使用了美國CDC官方估算數字計算。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<br />\n👉🏻 國衛委: 1月24日新型冠状病毒肺炎疫情<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/30QFU0o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F30QFU0o&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=13a3ad1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/30QFU0o</a><br />\n👉🏻 CDC: 2019-2020 U.S. flu season<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3aBABpT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3aBABpT&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=8ba5ade7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/3aBABpT</a><br />\n👉🏻 蘋果日報: 有患者無發燒 新病毒6日極速殺人<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2RkRLR6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2RkRLR6&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=6926fc2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2RkRLR6</a><br />\n👉🏻 中国每年8.8万人死于流感 <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/37r2cYM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37r2cYM&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=bec95c62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/37r2cYM</a>"},{"pid":"41ffeb3e854e1848298421584abe545d695b569e","tid":1838583,"uid":265902,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:32:17.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7755f3503103a185bc68e4e74b1194e708081cb3","tid":1838583,"uid":201238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:32:29.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"0d9bb0475111474f179da3ca50b8dd12a885158e","tid":1838583,"uid":265902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:32:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606779a8d5dd07a42fdf22ad874ab72182aa6719","tid":1838583,"uid":202724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:32:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nCCTVB做假"},{"pid":"18356a373c1c0236a6ba596049705a52ab54d8d7","tid":1838583,"uid":148355,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:33:17.000Z","msg":"唔怪之得呢段時間save hk班垃圾成日攞呢樣嘢打飛機"},{"pid":"df6d87e0b320d7ca1ebb704a16ef2c6081bee63d","tid":1838583,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:36:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護